719
00:51:22,538 --> 00:51:23,959
Share the stuff that's going to be most useful

720
00:51:23,979 --> 00:51:24,639
for the consultation.

721
00:51:26,821 --> 00:51:28,622
You also need to give them plenty of time to prepare,

